{"tid":1472692,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"道歉活動係條好橋，不過唔應該太卑微亦不宜出太多","createTime":"2019-08-14T15:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T11:16:50.000Z","uid":270871,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d1e8cbbd07c6a22372a81b70ebcb5a717c42b881","tid":1472692,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:46:49.000Z","msg":"首先同去咗機場道歉嘅手足講聲辛苦晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我純粹想俾一樣建議：<br />\n唔需要鞠躬<br />\n<br />\n尋晚機場犯嘅係小錯<br />\n做嘅嘢都係有理據只係部分手法唔好（除咗搞到立場記者同救護呢樣冇得兜之外）<br />\n唔需要咁卑微<br />\n我覺得不卑不亢咁致歉同解釋返件事就夠<br />\n<br />\n我哋唔係純粹嘅受害者可憐人<br />\n我哋係一旦贏咗就會手執香港權力嘅人<br />\n冇人會放心交個統治權俾班冇威嚴嘅兔仔<br />\n所以<span style=\"color: red;\">考慮抗爭者嘅尊嚴係好重要</span><br />\n無論如何，各有各做，尊重現場決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe1fb2ccc2cc5a99f1e96b90acd2c9aea9b67e7c","tid":1472692,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:47:09.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"ddcf9ccb232310e1cb9bbd98b4af4d9848e2d0e8","tid":1472692,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909272fa8bd251957b24c56d7cb5902954b5da94","tid":1472692,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90d4ce4d254ebc4c4b32176a67914280b4c0d2c","tid":1472692,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:53:27.000Z","msg":"不卑不亢不卑不亢"},{"pid":"42e20907d735764c8fe5d1160fcb3899699a83a9","tid":1472692,"uid":212217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:02:10.000Z","msg":"<strong>求推求推! 香港人可以試下noise making protest! </strong><br />\n<b